CONSOLE DISPLAY OPTIMISATION
============================

OS X
----

20 ms sleep
2-4 speed / 125 bpm module (crossroads)

no diff display
    terminal 100+% cpu
    player 24% cpu

diff display
    terminal 60-70% cpu
    player 12% cpu

display off
    player 5% cpu



WINDOWS
-------

much smoother framerate with optimisations

no diff display
    cpu total: 8-12%
    player: 3-4%

diff display
    cpu total: 3-7%
    player: 2-3%

display off
    player: 0-1%




